{"tid":2009233,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黃店推介】【香港永續經濟聯會】想印刷搵佢地！","createTime":"2020-05-09T15:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T15:20:14.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73c44e767acaf9298eac4b892ac6218f98f788e1","tid":2009233,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkbase.org/posts/2472104833100862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkbase.org%2Fposts%2F2472104833100862&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5165b052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkbase.org/posts/2472104833100862</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DR5W3Ln.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDR5W3Ln.png&h=baecb404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【#黃金企業】HKBASE團隊又出動拜訪黃企啦！今日我哋到訪首冠印刷有限公司，了解吓印刷服務呢個行業。<br />\n原來印刷唔係就咁撳個掣咁簡單，仲需要好多步驟以確保印刷質素、冇色差等等。大家平時要印卡片、搞活動需要印刷都可以搵佢地！如果有業務上嘅需要，亦可以直接搵佢哋傾生意㗎！面對疫情，我哋要一齊撐起黃企！<br />\n<br />\n公司名稱：首冠印刷有限公司 Crown Printing Co. Ltd.<br />\n公司電話：23424283<br />\n公司電郵：ken@crownprintinghk.com<br />\n<br />\n▋延伸閱讀<br />\n有關香港黃金經濟圈的思考筆記／方志恒<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/35SG9bT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35SG9bT&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=c80377bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/35SG9bT</a><br />\n【和你薦】黃企請留名：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30zDhj7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30zDhj7&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=2910572c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30zDhj7</a><br />\n<br />\n#黃金經濟圈 #黃金企業家 #黃色經濟圈 #黃店 #黃企 #黃懲罰 #YellowEconomy #香港人生意 #香港人引薦 #永續經濟 #香港自強 #香港人加油 #願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n香港永續經濟聯會：永續經濟．香港自強<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n1. Email：info@hkbase.org<br />\n2. Websi